ggplot(data = var_qual, 
       mapping = aes(qual)) + 
  geom_histogram(fill = "thistle", 
               colour = "black", 
               alpha = 0.3, 
               binwidth = 20) +
  xlim(30, 1000) +
  labs(title = "Variant Quality (YU_APseudo_1.1)") +
  theme_bw()


ggplot(data = var_qual2, 
       mapping = aes(qual)) + 
  geom_histogram(fill = "lightskyblue", 
               colour = "black", 
               alpha = 0.3, 
               binwidth = 20) +
  xlim(30, 1000) +
  labs(title = "Variant Quality (fAloSap.pri)") +
  theme_bw()

ggplot(data = var_depth, 
       mapping = aes(mean_depth)) +
  geom_histogram(fill = "thistle", 
               colour = "black", 
               alpha = 0.3, 
               binwidth = 0.1) +
  xlim(0, 10) +
  ylim(0, 1.25e+06) +
  labs(title = "Mean Variant Depth (YU_APseudo_1.1)") +
  theme_bw()


ggplot(data = var_depth2, 
       mapping = aes(mean_depth)) +

               colour = "black", 
               alpha = 0.3, 
               binwidth = 0.1) +
  xlim(0, 10) +
  ylim(0, 1.25e+06) +

ggplot(data = var_miss,
